Build-Depends: cdbs, debhelper (>= 5)
Standards-Version: 3.7.2

Package: distro-defaults
Architecture: all
Description: set various default options
 This package has much influence on the system and update behaviour of
 customized live linux utilities. Take care to keep sane settings for
 installed systems.

